# Omit `cpu-features` — it's an optionalDependency of ssh2 that fails to
# compile against Electron 42's V8 (the ExternalPointerTypeTag ABI changed).
# ssh2 falls back to its pure-JS crypto path without it, so functionally
# nothing is lost; this just keeps `electron-builder install-app-deps` from
# aborting the rebuild on the optional native module.
# See https://github.com/electron-userland/electron-builder/issues/3984
omit=cpu-features
